WEBVTT

00:32.920 --> 00:34.000
Who's there?

00:38.240 --> 00:39.080
Strategist Gongsun?

00:39.680 --> 00:41.000
It's the middle of the night.

00:41.080 --> 00:42.680
What are you looking for? I'll help you.

00:43.680 --> 00:45.240
That's classified military information.

00:46.240 --> 00:47.200
What classified information?

00:50.880 --> 00:52.320
I told you, it's classified.
Why do you keep asking?

00:52.400 --> 00:54.280
-Go away.
-Yes, sir.

00:55.120 --> 00:55.960
Go that way.

02:22.160 --> 02:23.200
Strategist.

02:26.000 --> 02:27.160
Come in.

02:28.240 --> 02:30.040
Strategist, it's already the fourth watch.

02:30.120 --> 02:31.920
You're wounded. Get some rest.

02:32.440 --> 02:34.000
I'll keep reviewing
the classified materials a while longer.

02:35.040 --> 02:36.320
-You may go.
-Yes, sir.

03:22.840 --> 03:24.000
Good.

03:24.080 --> 03:25.120
Very good.

03:26.560 --> 03:28.120
Ancestors left us a rule.

03:28.920 --> 03:30.400
When forging a fierce blade,

03:30.480 --> 03:32.480
it must taste blood
before it's truly born.

03:33.520 --> 03:36.040
Only then can it leave the forge

03:36.120 --> 03:39.640
to tame the spirit within,

03:39.720 --> 03:41.560
so it doesn't turn on its master.

03:41.640 --> 03:44.080
The Marquis has never believed
in such superstitious nonsense.

03:45.960 --> 03:46.800
Whose blood?

03:48.360 --> 03:49.800
Human blood is best.

04:14.600 --> 04:15.520
Come.

04:18.399 --> 04:19.360
Light the fire.

04:33.600 --> 04:37.400
Marquis, please treat
these two blades well.

04:51.400 --> 04:52.360
She is the one…

04:54.400 --> 04:56.120
who can fulfill these blades.

06:24.840 --> 06:28.880
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

06:50.600 --> 06:53.600
Young master, we can't hide for long.

06:53.680 --> 06:55.200
If it comes down to fighting to the death,

06:55.280 --> 06:57.000
I'll lead them away.

06:57.080 --> 06:58.920
You just focus on escaping.
Don't worry about me.

06:59.880 --> 07:01.160
Uncle Xun, don't rush.

07:02.840 --> 07:05.840
Look at these wheel tracks
on the main road.

07:05.920 --> 07:08.000
An army just passed through here.

07:11.040 --> 07:12.880
You mean we can ask for help?

07:12.960 --> 07:15.240
But what if it's Sui's army?

07:15.320 --> 07:16.680
We'd be walking right into their hands.

07:19.880 --> 07:21.120
I've read my fa…

07:21.920 --> 07:23.920
that person's scrolls before.

07:24.000 --> 07:25.720
It contains
the specifications for military vehicles

07:25.800 --> 07:27.520
from Chongzhou, Yanzhou, and Jizhou.

07:29.840 --> 07:32.120
These tracks belong to the Xie army.

07:36.440 --> 07:37.840
Young master, how old are you?

07:39.920 --> 07:41.640
-How old are you?
-Six.

07:43.160 --> 07:44.520
Still so young,

07:45.200 --> 07:46.520
yet you never forget what you see.

07:47.440 --> 07:49.240
Your talent is truly heaven-sent.

07:51.240 --> 07:53.240
So you are the chosen one after all.

07:53.840 --> 07:55.160
My teacher once taught me,

07:55.240 --> 07:57.120
when faced with two evils,
choose the lesser.

07:57.200 --> 07:58.960
Uncle Xun, you can take that gamble.

07:59.720 --> 08:00.640
Aren't you afraid?

08:01.520 --> 08:02.640
If we lose this gamble,

08:03.520 --> 08:05.160
we'll die with no place to be buried.

08:05.240 --> 08:08.520
Uncle Xun, remember, we're not fleeing.

08:08.600 --> 08:10.960
We're going to get reinforcements
to save my mother.

08:12.040 --> 08:14.640
Yes, sir. As you command.

08:52.840 --> 08:54.360
What time is it?

08:55.400 --> 08:58.480
It's midday. The sun's been up for ages.

08:59.000 --> 09:02.240
Sister, you've slept so long.

09:03.120 --> 09:04.400
This fish tastes so good.

09:06.240 --> 09:09.000
I couldn't sleep last night,
so I went to the river and caught it.

09:15.080 --> 09:16.040
You've got it all over your mouth.

09:20.000 --> 09:21.040
You enjoying that?

09:21.120 --> 09:23.080
So good. Zheng grilled it.

09:25.160 --> 09:27.120
How do you know it was he who grilled it?

09:27.200 --> 09:29.520
Back when Sister hadn't found me yet,

09:30.040 --> 09:32.400
Zheng grilled fish for me.
It tasted just like this.

09:34.960 --> 09:36.160
Then eat up.

09:36.680 --> 09:39.200
Sister, I miss Bao'er.

09:39.280 --> 09:41.160
And Pretty Lady too.

09:43.480 --> 09:44.720
I miss them too.

09:48.040 --> 09:49.840
That smells amazing.

09:51.840 --> 09:53.120
Master!

09:53.720 --> 09:54.920
You're here!

09:56.880 --> 09:58.880
Grandpa looks like a sage from a painting.

09:58.960 --> 10:01.240
Like the stone statue
in the Confucius temple.

10:01.320 --> 10:02.800
I look like Confucius?

10:03.440 --> 10:04.840
You flatter me too much.

10:05.520 --> 10:07.200
The older one is simple,

10:07.280 --> 10:09.920
but the little one has a sweet mouth.

10:10.000 --> 10:13.480
Come here, sweet little one.

10:13.560 --> 10:15.760
Let me take a good look at you.

10:25.720 --> 10:28.440
This child is blessed with good fortune.

10:30.480 --> 10:33.080
With you watching over her
in the first half of her life,

10:33.160 --> 10:36.200
the second half will bring her
great wealth and honor.

10:36.280 --> 10:37.760
Uncle Zhao said the same.

10:37.840 --> 10:39.280
He said her round face
means she's blessed.

10:39.360 --> 10:40.400
Zhao?

10:42.320 --> 10:45.160
His face-reading can't compare to mine.

10:46.760 --> 10:48.640
I wouldn't know how to compare.

10:48.720 --> 10:50.240
I just hope you're both right,

10:50.320 --> 10:51.720
that she stays healthy and happy.

10:52.320 --> 10:53.160
Good.

10:53.680 --> 10:56.400
Come, let me read your bones.

11:04.640 --> 11:08.840
This child,
her fate is too wealthy and noble.

11:09.720 --> 11:10.880
It's overwhelming.

11:11.680 --> 11:14.080
Naturally, her constitution
will be a bit weaker.

11:14.160 --> 11:17.680
But with you anchoring her,
that's heaven's will too.

11:19.320 --> 11:20.200
You don't understand?

11:23.400 --> 11:25.040
Before she comes of age,

11:25.120 --> 11:28.720
you must keep her by your side.

11:29.320 --> 11:30.440
Of course.

11:32.000 --> 11:33.000
Good.

11:33.880 --> 11:37.080
Girl, a few words from the heart.

11:39.520 --> 11:41.040
Come, Ning.

11:41.120 --> 11:42.720
Go play with Brother Jiu.

11:42.800 --> 11:43.760
Okay.

11:44.480 --> 11:45.840
Slow down.

11:51.640 --> 11:56.240
Last night, I heard you killed Shi Hu
with just three hammer blows.

11:56.320 --> 11:57.800
I was truly astonished.

11:57.880 --> 12:01.840
He was a fierce general,
renowned throughout the army.

12:02.720 --> 12:03.560
Two hammer blows.

12:03.640 --> 12:04.520
Two blows?

12:06.200 --> 12:10.960
I just found out you're some kind
of Minister or Grand Tutor.

12:11.040 --> 12:12.040
Anyway, someone really important.

12:12.120 --> 12:14.120
If Jin Yuanbao and the others knew

12:14.200 --> 12:16.880
they built a dam
with such a big figure like you,

12:16.960 --> 12:18.080
they'd never stop boasting about it.

12:19.520 --> 12:21.440
Are those rascals doing well?

12:21.520 --> 12:22.600
Still alive.

12:23.240 --> 12:25.560
Alive. That's good.

12:26.800 --> 12:30.120
Girl, let's get to the point.
I'll speak plainly.

12:31.080 --> 12:34.520
Someone has asked me
to take you as my adopted daughter.

12:35.240 --> 12:36.280
Adopted daughter?

12:37.280 --> 12:38.960
But I'm already your disciple.

12:39.960 --> 12:41.960
That's different.

12:47.800 --> 12:49.640
Xie Zheng sent you, didn't he?

12:59.560 --> 13:02.240
Grand Tutor, I appreciate your kindness,

13:03.240 --> 13:06.680
but I don't want to rely on anyone
to elevate my social ranks.

13:06.760 --> 13:09.200
I may just be
a pig-slaughtering girl from Lin'an,

13:09.280 --> 13:11.520
but I can support myself and my sister

13:11.600 --> 13:12.800
with my own two hands.

13:13.480 --> 13:17.080
I don't think there's anything shameful
about who I am.

13:18.920 --> 13:20.440
If he looks down on that,

13:21.400 --> 13:22.520
then so be it.

13:23.040 --> 13:24.600
I love Yan Zheng.

13:25.440 --> 13:26.880
I don't want to marry above myself
to the Marquis of Wu'an.

13:28.080 --> 13:29.800
This isn't some storybook.

13:29.880 --> 13:32.040
Sparrows don't just turn into phoenixes.

13:32.120 --> 13:34.880
Good. Well said.

13:35.520 --> 13:36.640
Rely on yourself.

13:36.720 --> 13:38.640
The strong stand on their own.

13:38.720 --> 13:42.640
But let me say a fair word
for my stubborn disciple.

13:42.720 --> 13:45.800
He never looked down on who you are.

13:46.320 --> 13:47.560
He just wants

13:48.160 --> 13:50.320
one more person to protect you.

13:51.160 --> 13:54.880
I may not be much,
but I have some small reputation.

13:55.560 --> 13:58.920
If anyone ever tries to harm you,
I'll protect you.

13:59.000 --> 14:01.080
Who would want to harm me?

14:02.320 --> 14:04.280
No one now doesn't mean no one ever.

14:04.360 --> 14:06.840
What if there is in the future?

14:08.360 --> 14:10.600
If someone really wants to harm me,

14:11.120 --> 14:12.880
would relying on a man really work?

14:14.080 --> 14:16.320
Or would your reputation
really protect me, Master?

14:17.520 --> 14:19.320
Even if you can protect me for a while,

14:20.200 --> 14:21.760
can you protect me for a lifetime?

14:21.840 --> 14:22.760
You…

14:23.400 --> 14:25.400
You… This girl…

14:25.480 --> 14:27.240
You see things even clearer than I do.

14:29.560 --> 14:32.680
A found jade pendant
must eventually be returned.

14:33.880 --> 14:37.400
When I saw him
as the majestic Marquis of Wu'an,

14:38.560 --> 14:39.640
I understood.

14:41.320 --> 14:42.920
I understood why he hid his identity.

14:44.280 --> 14:45.760
Why he wouldn't stay in Lin'an.

14:48.960 --> 14:50.360
You don't lack a father.

14:51.880 --> 14:55.480
But I lack a daughter.

14:55.560 --> 14:58.560
Otherwise, I'll end up alone forever.

14:59.960 --> 15:02.480
I want to take you as my adopted daughter

15:02.560 --> 15:05.280
because of the bond between us.

15:05.360 --> 15:07.760
If you accept me as your adoptive father,

15:07.840 --> 15:10.440
I'll treat you as my own flesh and blood,

15:10.520 --> 15:14.440
protect you, keep you safe
and happy for the rest of your life.

15:18.720 --> 15:19.800
Think it over carefully.

15:19.880 --> 15:21.720
I won't force you.

15:26.640 --> 15:28.040
The day we drew lots at the dam,

15:28.680 --> 15:30.640
you were protecting me with your own life.

15:31.680 --> 15:35.120
I also said I would take care of you
until the end.

15:36.040 --> 15:39.040
But if you insist on a formal bond…

15:44.000 --> 15:45.440
Adoptive Father,

15:46.040 --> 15:47.280
please accept your daughter's bow.

15:55.840 --> 15:58.760
Rise, please.

15:58.840 --> 16:00.160
Quickly, get up.

16:01.120 --> 16:03.680
You… You accept me
as your adoptive father?

16:03.760 --> 16:05.440
Good.

16:07.240 --> 16:09.720
Half a lifetime alone and lonely,

16:09.800 --> 16:11.400
I never thought,

16:11.480 --> 16:14.920
in the end, I'd gain
such a wonderful daughter.

16:19.600 --> 16:20.640
Daughter.

16:24.000 --> 16:25.160
I…

16:25.240 --> 16:29.040
I should give you a gift
to mark this bond,

16:29.560 --> 16:32.800
but… I have nothing of value.

16:34.080 --> 16:37.160
I know. I'll give you a courtesy name.

16:39.720 --> 16:41.240
You were born

16:41.920 --> 16:43.480
in the Year of the Tiger.

16:43.560 --> 16:44.920
Your given name, Changyu,

16:45.760 --> 16:48.120
means "virtuous and polished",

16:48.200 --> 16:51.280
but it suppresses your sharpness.

16:52.480 --> 16:54.160
I'll choose this one for you.

16:57.480 --> 16:59.560
"Shanjun".

17:00.760 --> 17:01.760
It means "Lord of the Mountain"?

17:04.200 --> 17:06.000
That's one interpretation.

17:06.599 --> 17:09.040
But it also has another meaning.

17:09.119 --> 17:12.720
The fierce tiger of the mountain.

17:12.800 --> 17:15.599
A tigress of the mountain.

17:17.880 --> 17:19.040
Now that's good.

17:19.119 --> 17:20.839
Much better than Lord Li's suggestion.

17:21.680 --> 17:23.119
You child,

17:23.200 --> 17:25.960
why do you always pick
the worst way to say things?

17:29.320 --> 17:31.480
Shanjun.

17:32.400 --> 17:34.800
XIE

17:34.880 --> 17:37.520
MARQUIS OF WU'AN

18:08.240 --> 18:10.000
Though we won this battle,

18:10.840 --> 18:12.840
the casualties were heavy.

18:13.480 --> 18:17.240
The upcoming battle at Lucheng
will be even harder.

18:18.280 --> 18:22.240
The Yanzhou army is about

18:23.040 --> 18:24.800
to march for Lucheng.

18:26.880 --> 18:30.680
Will you go with my stubborn disciple?

18:35.920 --> 18:36.840
No.

18:39.240 --> 18:41.120
Now that I know he's the Marquis of Wu'an,

18:42.280 --> 18:44.520
I don't need to worry
about his safety anymore.

18:47.120 --> 18:48.240
I want to leave.

18:49.440 --> 18:50.840
He has his affairs,

18:51.720 --> 18:53.000
I have my life.

18:54.200 --> 18:56.320
I want to help the people of Lin'an
who've been displaced

18:57.080 --> 18:58.720
find their way home safely.

18:59.600 --> 19:01.160
Families reunited,

19:03.400 --> 19:06.840
back to work, back to meals,

19:07.720 --> 19:09.280
living their simple lives well.

19:10.400 --> 19:12.240
With your achievements,

19:12.320 --> 19:13.760
you could be appointed Commander,

19:14.520 --> 19:16.440
as a sixth-ranked official.

19:16.960 --> 19:20.920
The first female commander
in all of Dayin.

19:21.000 --> 19:24.640
Such honor,
are you willing to give that up?

19:27.360 --> 19:28.480
Adoptive Father,

19:30.920 --> 19:33.240
I don't like the feeling
of killing at all.

19:33.320 --> 19:34.200
True.

19:36.160 --> 19:38.240
The rebels who threaten Dayin
deserve to die.

19:39.200 --> 19:41.240
But when I see them on the battlefield,

19:41.320 --> 19:44.080
terrified, wailing, kneeling,
and begging for mercy,

19:44.760 --> 19:47.920
I think of Uncle Zhao
and Mr. Jin being taken away.

19:48.800 --> 19:51.240
I think of Mrs. Kang's youngest son,
killed in battle.

19:51.840 --> 19:54.040
I think of the innocent people of Lin'an.

19:54.640 --> 19:56.440
None of them wanted war.

19:57.840 --> 19:59.320
But because of war,

20:00.560 --> 20:02.280
they had no choice but to go die.

20:03.320 --> 20:04.880
This kind of pain…

20:06.200 --> 20:07.840
I don't want to see it anymore.

20:14.640 --> 20:15.560
You want to leave?

20:17.440 --> 20:20.000
You know that husband of yours
and his stubborn temper, don't you?

20:20.080 --> 20:21.480
If you tell him,

20:21.560 --> 20:23.440
he'll tie you to him if he has to.

20:24.320 --> 20:25.640
I know.

20:25.720 --> 20:28.360
That's exactly why
I'm asking for your help.

20:29.800 --> 20:31.000
There's too much

20:31.920 --> 20:33.440
between us that's unresolved.

20:34.040 --> 20:36.400
But right now,
I have more important things to do.

20:36.480 --> 20:38.080
What's so important?

20:39.040 --> 20:40.600
I need to find a dear friend of mine.

20:41.520 --> 20:44.320
Only when she and her child are safe
will I be at ease.

20:47.120 --> 20:50.280
If it were any other woman, I'd stop her.

20:50.960 --> 20:52.600
But you're Fan Changyu.

20:52.680 --> 20:54.360
You killed Shi Hu with two hammer blows.

20:55.520 --> 20:56.440
In all of Dayin,

20:56.520 --> 20:58.200
besides the Marquis of Wu'an,

20:58.280 --> 20:59.560
I can't think of a third.

21:01.800 --> 21:03.760
Is there anything else
I can help you with?

21:05.080 --> 21:06.040
Actually, yes.

21:06.560 --> 21:11.080
Please, help me send Ning and Uncle Zhao
from the Wu River camp.

21:11.160 --> 21:14.680
Send them both
back to Jizhou, to Auntie Zhao.

21:18.640 --> 21:20.440
You're not really a physician,

21:21.120 --> 21:23.880
and your name isn't Qi Bengong, is it?

21:24.520 --> 21:26.040
Yan Zheng is the Marquis of Wu'an.

21:27.040 --> 21:28.480
You're close with him.

21:29.560 --> 21:31.600
You must be someone
of wealth and status too.

21:34.320 --> 21:35.800
You'll know one day.

21:37.000 --> 21:37.960
But for now,

21:38.880 --> 21:40.680
you and I are just comrades
who fought together.

21:44.640 --> 21:45.760
Take care on your journey.

21:47.080 --> 21:48.240
Remember,

21:49.480 --> 21:50.640
stay safe.

22:00.280 --> 22:01.360
You take care too.

22:06.800 --> 22:08.320
The road to Lucheng,

22:08.400 --> 22:10.240
Prince Changxin has likely
set up ambushes long ago.

22:13.200 --> 22:14.800
Since we can't face him head-on,

22:15.400 --> 22:17.960
why not go around from behind?

22:18.560 --> 22:21.800
That way, the journey is twice as long.

22:24.440 --> 22:26.080
We must depart before dawn.

22:26.760 --> 22:29.080
Okay. I'll pass the order.
We set out at the fifth watch.

22:30.280 --> 22:32.480
Marquis! The Marchioness, she's gone.

22:32.560 --> 22:34.480
We found this letter left in her tent.

22:36.080 --> 22:38.120
TO THE MARQUIS OF WU'AN

22:41.760 --> 22:43.520
I HAVE THINGS TO DO
DO NOT LOOK FOR ME. CHANGYU

22:47.480 --> 22:49.760
-Xie Jiu, saddle a horse.
-Yes, sir.

22:58.560 --> 22:59.520
Fan Changyu!

23:05.000 --> 23:05.880
The Marquis of Wu'an is coming.

23:06.400 --> 23:08.080
We'll hold him off for you.

23:08.800 --> 23:09.680
No need.

23:10.560 --> 23:12.160
I didn't explain myself clearly.

23:13.200 --> 23:14.040
You go ahead.

23:14.120 --> 23:15.520
We'll wait for you up ahead.

23:27.880 --> 23:28.840
Fan Changyu.

23:29.360 --> 23:32.520
Why would you rather leave a letter and go
than stay with me?

23:36.040 --> 23:37.520
Why won't you let yourself love me?

23:38.760 --> 23:40.520
What have I, Xie Zheng, done wrong?

23:49.080 --> 23:51.080
How could I not love you?

23:51.880 --> 23:53.360
If I didn't love you,

23:55.080 --> 23:56.080
would I have come looking for you?

23:57.400 --> 23:58.920
Would I have worried about you
getting hurt?

23:59.000 --> 24:00.560
Would I have gone to battle in your place?

24:04.800 --> 24:06.080
The one you love…

24:07.400 --> 24:08.480
is Yan Zheng.

24:10.120 --> 24:11.360
I've thought it through.

24:11.880 --> 24:14.880
Whether you're Yan Zheng or Xie Zheng,
I love you all the same.

24:16.320 --> 24:17.240
Are you just…

24:18.680 --> 24:19.600
trying to placate me?

24:19.680 --> 24:21.120
I'm not placating you.

24:21.200 --> 24:22.360
These are all my true feelings.

24:23.960 --> 24:25.160
When you were Yan Zheng,

24:25.840 --> 24:29.000
all we worried about was daily life.

24:29.680 --> 24:31.800
You'd copy texts
and write essays to earn money.

24:33.280 --> 24:35.240
I'd slaughter pigs and sell pork.

24:36.160 --> 24:37.360
When difficulties came,

24:38.120 --> 24:40.960
we supported each other and got through.

24:42.480 --> 24:44.200
But Xie Zheng,
you're the Marquis of Wu'an now.

24:46.360 --> 24:47.760
I can't help you with anything.

24:49.760 --> 24:51.040
I don't know…

24:52.120 --> 24:54.200
what keeps you busy, what troubles you.

24:56.040 --> 24:57.200
My mother told me,

24:57.800 --> 24:58.840
for a marriage to last,

24:59.880 --> 25:03.720
husband and wife
must understand and support each other.

25:05.280 --> 25:06.320
The unhappy couples,

25:07.200 --> 25:08.960
they're the ones
who never learned to understand

25:09.040 --> 25:10.080
before their lives together ended.

25:11.080 --> 25:12.280
Their feelings

25:13.040 --> 25:14.440
were worn away long ago.

25:15.640 --> 25:16.960
I don't want that for us.

25:21.160 --> 25:22.280
Changyu,

25:23.000 --> 25:25.600
status is an illusion.

25:26.760 --> 25:28.880
What matters most
is that we understand each other.

25:28.960 --> 25:30.880
Of course I know that.

25:34.400 --> 25:35.640
That day,

25:37.160 --> 25:39.520
I actually thought about
cutting ties with you completely.

25:40.600 --> 25:43.880
But when you talked about
our life in Lin'an,

25:43.960 --> 25:47.040
the little moments, how you wanted
to go back with me and rebuild our home,

25:50.320 --> 25:52.360
I'm not made of stone.

25:53.800 --> 25:55.040
I was moved.

25:55.760 --> 25:56.880
I couldn't bear to let go.

26:02.200 --> 26:05.840
But right now,
there's something I must do.

26:06.520 --> 26:08.040
I have to go save Qian.

26:11.560 --> 26:12.480
But you know

26:13.480 --> 26:15.400
the people who took Yu Qianqian
are no ordinary foes.

26:15.920 --> 26:17.120
On your own,

26:18.040 --> 26:19.280
you might not be able to save her.

26:19.360 --> 26:20.680
I have to try to find out.

26:25.320 --> 26:26.240
How about this?

26:27.360 --> 26:30.040
I'll avenge what happened
in Lin'an for you.

26:30.560 --> 26:31.720
I'll find the people you're looking for.

26:32.560 --> 26:35.320
I'll rescue Yu Qianqian for you.

26:35.920 --> 26:37.880
You don't have to take the risk. Okay?

26:40.960 --> 26:42.240
I like you.

26:43.960 --> 26:45.960
But I can't spend the rest of my life
relying on you.

26:47.200 --> 26:49.680
If I did, I wouldn't be me anymore.

26:54.480 --> 26:55.480
Okay.

26:57.560 --> 26:58.600
I know.

26:59.240 --> 27:00.640
Once you've made up your mind,

27:01.360 --> 27:03.040
you won't easily change it.

27:20.440 --> 27:21.680
Your Highness,

27:23.240 --> 27:25.200
may I come in?

27:28.120 --> 27:28.960
Come in.

27:34.920 --> 27:37.840
Headmaster, what brings you here
so suddenly?

27:38.680 --> 27:39.520
Your Highness,

27:40.440 --> 27:41.400
your shoes.

27:47.880 --> 27:48.800
You fixed them?

27:51.600 --> 27:53.680
A soldier on patrol last night
happened to find them.

27:53.760 --> 27:55.520
I made some small repairs.

27:56.360 --> 27:58.400
I hope you don't mind.

28:01.920 --> 28:04.000
Headmaster, don't bother
with such trifles.

28:04.800 --> 28:05.920
I won't be grateful.

28:19.680 --> 28:20.760
I'm leaving.

28:31.840 --> 28:33.960
Headmaster, don't try
these little tricks on me.

28:38.760 --> 28:40.200
What's… What's wrong with you?

28:46.640 --> 28:47.560
It's almost dawn.

28:48.440 --> 28:49.520
I have to go now,

28:50.080 --> 28:51.320
or I won't catch up to them.

29:02.560 --> 29:03.400
Then say it.

29:04.720 --> 29:05.600
Say you like me.

29:12.040 --> 29:12.880
Say it.

29:56.200 --> 29:58.760
Find an elite squad.
Discreetly protect Fan Changyu.

29:58.840 --> 29:59.760
Yes, sir.

30:02.600 --> 30:04.280
Headmaster, you're wounded this badly.

30:04.960 --> 30:06.400
Why didn't you say anything before?

30:07.480 --> 30:09.000
When I thought you were tricking me,

30:10.000 --> 30:11.360
why didn't you tell the truth?

30:12.520 --> 30:13.520
Before…

30:15.520 --> 30:16.800
I did deceive you.

30:18.000 --> 30:19.280
So today,

30:20.520 --> 30:22.680
I am too ashamed to make excuses.

30:29.640 --> 30:30.560
I'll…

30:31.760 --> 30:33.960
find some herbs to treat it.

30:34.480 --> 30:35.520
Your Highness, rest early.

30:37.440 --> 30:40.280
I am calling the shots
for your condition as the physician.

30:40.880 --> 30:41.880
Turn around.

30:42.400 --> 30:43.760
Turn around!

30:51.000 --> 30:53.520
At the academy, your word is law.

30:53.600 --> 30:55.040
On the battlefield, you're brave and wise.

30:55.640 --> 30:57.480
Why are you so careless
when it comes to yourself?

31:04.320 --> 31:06.280
What are you smiling about?
You're still wounded.

31:06.360 --> 31:07.480
No, I'm ticklish.

31:08.480 --> 31:10.400
You're about to die
and you're still laughing?

31:12.120 --> 31:13.040
I…

31:15.600 --> 31:18.280
I want to say… My feelings for you

31:19.680 --> 31:20.840
are like my injury.

31:22.800 --> 31:23.880
It seemed I deceived you,

31:24.800 --> 31:27.520
but it wasn't really my intention.

31:29.000 --> 31:29.840
Do you understand?

31:34.760 --> 31:36.600
-Let me be direct. I--
-Strategist,

31:39.640 --> 31:40.560
the Marquis returned.

31:43.600 --> 31:46.240
Even if the sky falls,
I'm finishing what I have to say.

31:46.320 --> 31:47.400
Come back and tell me.

31:48.600 --> 31:49.680
I'll wait for you.

31:58.680 --> 32:01.200
General Shi Yi, please inform the Marquis

32:01.800 --> 32:02.960
that the Strategist has internal injuries

32:03.040 --> 32:04.280
and shouldn't overexert himself.

32:06.520 --> 32:08.360
If his condition worsens after he returns,

32:08.880 --> 32:10.280
I'll hold him accountable.

32:10.360 --> 32:11.240
Yes.

32:12.360 --> 32:14.200
Then… I'll go now.

32:28.280 --> 32:29.520
You got her back?

32:29.600 --> 32:30.800
She's gone.

32:30.880 --> 32:32.080
She has her own thoughts.

32:32.160 --> 32:33.000
I respect her for it.

32:35.280 --> 32:36.400
This Mrs. Fan,

32:36.480 --> 32:39.080
to make the mighty Marquis of Wu'an
so dejected,

32:39.840 --> 32:40.800
she's quite something.

32:44.000 --> 32:45.480
The Grand Princess
is returning to the capital.

32:46.360 --> 32:48.520
I'm leaving the task
of protecting her to you.

32:49.120 --> 32:51.120
The Grand Princess has already agreed

32:51.200 --> 32:52.560
to send Ning back to Lin'an with Mrs. Fan.

32:52.640 --> 32:55.440
After that, whether she chooses
to stay in the capital

32:55.520 --> 32:56.880
or remain in the military camp,

32:56.960 --> 32:58.160
I'll respect her for it too.

33:00.000 --> 33:01.680
That's not what you said before.

33:01.760 --> 33:04.480
When Li Huai'an
was investigating me in Lin'an,

33:04.560 --> 33:06.440
he soon returned to the capital to meet
the Grand Princess for a matchmaking.

33:07.720 --> 33:08.960
That was your doing, wasn't it?

33:12.080 --> 33:13.280
Yes…

33:14.680 --> 33:15.760
and no.

33:18.280 --> 33:19.680
When feelings surge in the heart,

33:20.320 --> 33:21.400
they can't be controlled by will.

33:23.120 --> 33:24.600
Better to stop them before they sprout,

33:25.480 --> 33:26.880
to avoid falling into
the quagmire of love.

33:29.280 --> 33:32.360
Informing Empress Dowager An
about her life at the academy,

33:32.440 --> 33:34.160
that was indeed my doing.

33:34.240 --> 33:37.640
As for the matchmaking between
the Grand Princess and Li Huai'an,

33:38.480 --> 33:40.520
that truly was unexpected.

33:41.600 --> 33:43.160
Given Empress Dowager An's nature,

33:43.880 --> 33:45.840
she would never consent.

33:47.520 --> 33:48.720
This is the last time Your Highness

33:48.800 --> 33:50.760
has personally prepared medicinal food
for Master Gongsun.

33:52.960 --> 33:53.800
You all go ahead.

33:53.880 --> 33:55.320
My horse is fast. I'll catch up shortly.

34:01.040 --> 34:02.000
Let's move out.

34:06.400 --> 34:07.280
All troops, listen up.

34:07.880 --> 34:09.480
Move out to Lucheng.

34:09.560 --> 34:10.440
-Yes.
-Yes.

34:17.120 --> 34:18.040
MARQUIS WU'AN

34:23.719 --> 34:29.120
LUCHENG WESTERN SUBURB MANOR

34:39.880 --> 34:42.159
‎PRINCE CHANGXIN, SUI TUO

34:43.800 --> 34:44.679
Father.

34:58.800 --> 35:01.080
I never should have
believed your nonsense.

35:01.160 --> 35:02.840
What "infallible plans"?

35:03.360 --> 35:04.920
Now we're retreating at every step.

35:05.520 --> 35:07.680
Not only did we lose
a great general like Shi Hu,

35:08.600 --> 35:10.720
we nearly cost Yuanqing his life as well.

35:16.880 --> 35:17.920
What?

35:18.480 --> 35:19.320
You don't agree?

35:19.400 --> 35:20.960
Do you think I'm wronging you?

35:28.480 --> 35:29.880
When you were young,

35:30.680 --> 35:32.120
you were bright and cheerful.

35:32.200 --> 35:34.720
One fire turned you into
what you are today.

35:39.320 --> 35:40.960
Let me make this clear to you now.

35:42.000 --> 35:44.560
Even if something happens to Yuanqing,

35:45.200 --> 35:47.720
the throne will never be yours.

35:50.280 --> 35:52.280
I have never coveted the throne,

35:52.840 --> 35:54.360
nor have I any desire
to compete with Yuanqing.

35:55.440 --> 35:56.760
If these words are false in the slightest,

35:57.360 --> 35:58.880
-may heaven strike me down.
-Big brother,

36:00.400 --> 36:02.160
do brothers need
to make vows between them?

36:03.400 --> 36:04.560
Why curse yourself like this?

36:05.280 --> 36:06.120
Come.

36:06.640 --> 36:09.160
Yuanqing. This is wartime.

36:09.680 --> 36:10.560
Remember your position.

36:10.640 --> 36:13.560
Father, with the enemy at our gates,
can we drop the formalities?

36:13.640 --> 36:15.120
It's just the three of us here.

36:16.320 --> 36:18.440
If outsiders learn that our own family
is fighting amongst ourselves,

36:19.120 --> 36:20.280
they'll seize the chance to cause chaos.

36:21.400 --> 36:23.800
Even the wisest makes mistakes.

36:24.880 --> 36:27.080
Big brother did his best
against Xie Zheng.

36:28.560 --> 36:30.840
If he hadn't sent Shi Yue to rescue me,

36:31.440 --> 36:33.960
Xie Zheng would have tied me up and used
me to threaten you on the battlefield.

36:37.120 --> 36:38.840
Children are nothing but debts.

36:44.480 --> 36:45.520
Yuanhuai,

36:47.480 --> 36:49.280
go and reorganize the logistics.

36:50.280 --> 36:51.280
The Chongzhou army…

36:53.800 --> 36:55.480
cannot afford a third defeat.

36:57.200 --> 36:58.120
Yes, Father.

37:11.800 --> 37:15.400
Ever since that fire 17 years ago
left him scarred,

37:16.320 --> 37:19.160
he turned into a person
as stubborn and hard as stone,

37:19.240 --> 37:20.880
erratic, paranoid,

37:21.680 --> 37:23.600
as if possessed by some evil spirit.

37:24.200 --> 37:26.000
Father, please don't blame big brother.

37:26.520 --> 37:30.120
Anyone who suffers such a great ordeal
would inevitably change.

37:31.600 --> 37:33.120
Big brother has always been
kind and good to us.

37:33.200 --> 37:34.560
He's never had the slightest ill intent.

37:36.640 --> 37:38.000
I hope you'll see the truth.

37:48.800 --> 37:49.880
Sui Tuo,

37:51.480 --> 37:53.440
I truly don't want your throne.

37:54.520 --> 37:55.600
What I want…

37:58.280 --> 38:00.320
is your life. And your son's.

38:20.240 --> 38:21.000
Charge.

38:35.960 --> 38:37.040
Bao'er.

38:37.800 --> 38:40.160
Run! Go, go!

38:49.000 --> 38:50.080
Here, take this.

38:50.160 --> 38:53.080
If you ever run into danger, blow it,

38:53.160 --> 38:54.680
and someone will come to protect you.

39:08.920 --> 39:10.160
Bao'er.

39:36.560 --> 39:37.600
Fall back!

39:41.400 --> 39:42.960
We're from Jizhou.

39:43.040 --> 39:44.800
Not… Not the Chongzhou army.

39:53.600 --> 39:54.360
Bao'er.

40:00.240 --> 40:02.080
Uncle Yan.

40:03.040 --> 40:04.000
Are you alright?

40:09.000 --> 40:12.200
Uncle Yan, I'm so scared.

40:12.720 --> 40:15.280
The bad men took my mother away.

40:15.360 --> 40:16.480
It's okay.

40:16.560 --> 40:17.760
Everything will be okay.

40:23.800 --> 40:26.920
LUCHENG WESTERN SUBURB MANOR

40:27.000 --> 40:27.920
SUI

40:45.880 --> 40:46.800
Miss me?

40:55.480 --> 40:56.560
What are you standing there for?

40:56.640 --> 40:57.600
Come, sit.

41:09.280 --> 41:14.080
I personally made my specialty,
Snow-Cleared Broth.

41:18.560 --> 41:19.480
Give it a try.

41:25.880 --> 41:26.840
You didn't…

41:27.600 --> 41:29.320
poison this soup, did you?

41:33.440 --> 41:34.360
You scared?

42:00.400 --> 42:01.640
Even if it's poisoned,

42:02.840 --> 42:04.320
if you gave it to me,

42:05.160 --> 42:06.400
I'd drink it.

42:08.440 --> 42:09.320
Good.

42:10.360 --> 42:12.320
Then next time, I really will poison it.

42:20.600 --> 42:23.520
I'd drink it gladly.

42:41.360 --> 42:42.720
Just now, for a moment,

42:43.800 --> 42:45.120
I almost felt…

42:46.280 --> 42:47.720
that a life like this…

42:49.880 --> 42:50.800
wouldn't be so bad.

43:04.920 --> 43:06.560
If our army hadn't taken the detour,

43:06.640 --> 43:07.960
we wouldn't have run into you.

43:13.640 --> 43:16.520
Truly, fortune favors the brave.

43:19.920 --> 43:20.760
Untie him.

43:28.440 --> 43:29.280
Mr. Zhao,

43:29.960 --> 43:31.680
you've been so hard to find.

43:32.400 --> 43:34.040
I owe the Marquis my life.

43:34.920 --> 43:36.880
If there's any use for me,

43:36.960 --> 43:39.360
I'll serve with all my heart,
even if it costs me my life.

43:40.280 --> 43:42.720
That's exactly what you said
when you came to Lin'an

43:42.800 --> 43:43.960
looking for me last year.

43:45.000 --> 43:46.120
Please calm your anger, Marquis.

43:46.640 --> 43:48.520
I had no choice.

43:49.320 --> 43:52.480
That 200,000 dan of grain,
it truly was a trap.

43:53.000 --> 43:54.280
But fortunately, you saw through it,

43:54.880 --> 43:57.200
so those scoundrels
had no chance to exploit it.

43:57.280 --> 44:00.440
Back then, you told me
you worked for the Eastern Palace.

44:01.200 --> 44:02.760
Was that true or false?

44:04.520 --> 44:06.480
My mother, Nanny Lan,

44:07.320 --> 44:09.920
was once the most capable maid
to Crown Princess Chengde.

44:10.600 --> 44:12.800
When she came of age,
she was fortunate to leave the palace.

44:13.440 --> 44:15.000
On the surface, she married my father,

44:15.880 --> 44:18.280
but in truth, she secretly managed

44:18.360 --> 44:20.000
the Crown Princess Chengde's assets
outside the palace.

44:21.280 --> 44:24.400
Mistress, this room seems a bit dark.

44:25.000 --> 44:26.720
Shall I light two more lamps for you?

44:29.320 --> 44:32.000
That fire in the Eastern Palace,
it was set by the Crown Princess herself.

44:32.960 --> 44:35.960
To give the Crown Prince's eldest son
a chance to survive.

44:40.040 --> 44:43.000
Then who exactly
wanted to harm the Eastern Palace?

44:44.360 --> 44:45.840
I don't know.

44:45.920 --> 44:47.760
My mother only received
the Crown Princess's

44:47.840 --> 44:49.600
personal letter after the fire.

44:50.200 --> 44:52.920
But the letter said nothing
about who did it.

44:53.880 --> 44:56.560
Master, spare me!
I truly didn't know you were here.

44:58.040 --> 45:00.240
The Crown Prince's eldest son
is still alive, isn't he?

45:00.320 --> 45:01.320
Yes.

45:02.160 --> 45:03.600
He is now…

45:04.240 --> 45:06.240
Prince Changxin's eldest son.

45:06.840 --> 45:08.360
Sui Yuanhuai.

45:12.840 --> 45:15.120
END CREDIT SCENE

45:30.600 --> 45:31.720
On your body…

45:33.360 --> 45:34.920
there's more than just
sword and axe wounds.

45:40.680 --> 45:41.560
What's wrong?

45:43.960 --> 45:45.400
It must hurt a lot, doesn't it?

45:48.000 --> 45:48.920
It doesn't hurt.

45:50.400 --> 45:51.960
You're just a young lady.

45:52.840 --> 45:54.240
Being wounded like this,

45:55.000 --> 45:56.520
how could it not hurt?

46:04.640 --> 46:06.680
You… You're hurt here too.

46:06.760 --> 46:08.280
It's all red.

46:09.640 --> 46:11.960
Probably got banged up
on the battlefield too.

46:15.760 --> 46:16.640
Doesn't seem like it.

46:17.680 --> 46:20.200
The other bruises
on your body are dark purple.

46:21.320 --> 46:24.840
This one injury here looks fresh,
like it just happened.

46:25.720 --> 46:26.760
Strange.

46:27.280 --> 46:29.120
I've never seen anything like it
in the medical texts.

46:30.840 --> 46:33.120
It just happened.

46:46.880 --> 46:49.360
That wound was probably from falling

46:49.440 --> 46:50.360
and hitting a stone too.

49:34.400 --> 49:37.920
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS FILM

49:38.000 --> 49:38.840
Subtitle translation by: Wanjiao Song
